Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* position with *Uber Technologies*. I bring over three years of professional experience in distributed systems, backend engineering, and production-grade software development, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

